 Victor的VRChat音乐现场“MAGICAL JUKE BOX”将举行，Kami Hirose和VTuber将出现https://www.moguravr.com/magical-juke-box-vrchat/ノンジャンル人生 Thu, 16 May 2024 06:15:00 +0000 VRChatVTuberメタバースMAGICAL JUKE BOXVictor https://www.moguravr.com/?p=251154 <p> Victor的Metaverse音乐现场“MAGICAL JUKE BOX”将于6月15日星期六、6月23日星期日、6月30日星期日在VRChat举行为期3天。 “神奇点唱机”是 JVC Kenwood [...]</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/magical-juke-box-vrchat/">Victor 的 VRChat 音乐直播“MAGICAL JUKE BOX”即将举行 Kami Hirose 和 VTuber</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上。</p> ; <p> <a href="https://www.victor.jp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Victor</a>的Metaverse音乐现场<strong>“MAGICAL JUKE BOX”</strong>将于6月15日星期六、6月23日星期日、6月30日星期日在<a href="https://hello.vrchat.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">VRChat</a>举行为期3天。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/71eb73d6aa2be5072c778f4736a747ad-kix.lyv22cinevda-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/71eb73d6aa2be5072c778f4736a747ad-kix.lyv22cinevda-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/71eb73d6aa2be5072c778f4736a747ad-kix.lyv22cinevda-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/71eb73d6aa2be5072c778f4736a747ad-kix.lyv22cinevda-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/71eb73d6aa2be5072c778f4736a747ad-kix.lyv22cinevda-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p> “MAGICAL JUKE BOX”是JVC Kenwood主办的首个虚拟音乐节，由曾参与虚拟三丽鸥音乐节的Gugenka负责付费门票系统。除了艺术家Kami <a href="https://twitter.com/kohmi" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hirose</a>的化身<strong>“Kami 2-chan”之外，</strong>活跃在虚拟世界的总共8位受欢迎的VTuber也将出现。</p><p>在仿照复古风格电唱机的“现场场地”中，Omega Sisters<strong>与 Honwaka Band</strong>和<a href="https://www.youtube.com/@omesis" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Asano</strong></a>一起表演了 Kami <a href="https://twitter.com/asanoruri" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Hirose</strong></a>创作的主题曲“Hello You, Hello me”，以及“Kami No. 2-chan”。如<a href="https://twitter.com/asanoruri" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>瑠璃</strong></a>热情地歌唱。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/71eb73d6aa2be5072c778f4736a747ad-kix.zgn68s3y9ilp-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/71eb73d6aa2be5072c778f4736a747ad-kix.zgn68s3y9ilp-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/71eb73d6aa2be5072c778f4736a747ad-kix.zgn68s3y9ilp-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/71eb73d6aa2be5072c778f4736a747ad-kix.zgn68s3y9ilp-300x98.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/71eb73d6aa2be5072c778f4736a747ad-kix.zgn68s3y9ilp-768x251.webp 768w" width="1000" height="327" /></a></p><p>此外，在这次现场活动之前，从 6 月 7 日（星期五）起，将在 VRChat 上向公众开放一个免费的特殊世界。该设计以Victor品牌角色“Nipper”出现的图画书的世界观为基础，想象了一个坐落在被森林和湖泊包围的宁静山丘上的小镇。除了“现场会场”之外，还有展示过去的音响产品的“音乐咖啡馆”，以及耳机、收音机、移动电源等产品体验区补给品。</p><h2>演员</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/71eb73d6aa2be5072c778f4736a747ad-kix.7mdnd0bt1t49-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/71eb73d6aa2be5072c778f4736a747ad-kix.7mdnd0bt1t49-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/71eb73d6aa2be5072c778f4736a747ad-kix.7mdnd0bt1t49-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/71eb73d6aa2be5072c778f4736a747ad-kix.7mdnd0bt1t49-300x135.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/71eb73d6aa2be5072c778f4736a747ad-kix.7mdnd0bt1t49-768x345.webp 768w" width="1000" height="449" /></a><br />・神二号 ・Omega Sisters with Honwaka Band ・浅野琉璃</p><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/05/71eb73d6aa2be5072c778f4736a747ad-kix.u9fr5eq637yl-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img 